<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about the mission, history, and community impact of the Joe Rossi Hall of Fame." canonicalPath="/about/">
  <PageHero title="About The Joe Rossi Hall of Fame" intro="Honoring the individuals whose dedication, hard work, and contributions have made a lasting impact on the game of baseball." />
  <section class="section"><div class="container grid grid-2">
    <article class="surface">
      <p class="kicker">Our history</p>
      <h2>Joe Rossi's example became a tradition.</h2>
      <p>Founded in 1989, the Hall of Fame was established to recognize the lifelong contributions of Joe Rossi—a living legend whose leadership and passion helped shape the landscape of high school umpiring in Colorado.</p>
      <p>Joe Rossi is a leader, mentor, and icon in Colorado high school baseball. The Hall of Fame preserves his legacy alongside the stories of others who strengthened the game and its officiating community.</p>
    </article>
    <img src="/images/joe_rossi_first_pitch.jpeg" alt="Joe Rossi throwing a ceremonial first pitch" width="800" height="600" style="width:100%;height:100%;max-height:360px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:14px" />
  </div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container grid grid-3">
    <article class="card"><h2>Mission Statement</h2><p>Our mission is to recognize and celebrate the outstanding achievements of individuals who have made a difference in high school umpiring. By honoring them, we aim to inspire the next generation of leaders, mentors, and change-makers.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h2>Inductees</h2><p>Inductees are chosen for outstanding contributions to high school umpiring. Each has demonstrated exceptional leadership, dedication, and a lasting impact on the community.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h2>Looking Ahead</h2><p>JRHOF remains committed to expanding the Hall of Fame, preserving its history, and honoring more exceptional individuals who have contributed to the sport.</p></article>
  </div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container surface"><p class="kicker">Get involved</p><h2>Be part of the Hall of Fame legacy.</h2><p>Your support can help JRHOF continue to recognize outstanding individuals and inspire future generations. Whether through donations, volunteering, contributing historical materials, or attending events, your involvement makes a difference.</p><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/donate/">Support JRHOF</a><a class="button button-secondary" href="/contact/">Contact the Hall of Fame</a></div></div></section>
